column5: Looking for a nice lodge on Gullrock. Going in September.

mda, Personally, I don't think you can go wrong at any of the resorts on Gullrock. I have been going to Gullrock for 28 years and have stayed at a number of the resorts. A lot depends on what type of boat you will be fishing out of and how far you are wanting to run to get to your favorite fishing spots.
